title: Beige Backstage: The Complete Show
description:
For Beige's monthly show in February, we put together a sketch show that turned into a short play that was, itself, about a sketch show. We've included the entire show here.

Written and Performed by Beige:
Alene Latimer, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, Jon Bershad, Jonathan Marballi, Kelly Hudson, Kerry O'Brien, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Langan Kingsley, Lisa Kleinman, Ryan Hunter, Zack Phillips

Featuring:
Alan Starzinski, Jim Santangeli, Emily Wallace

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, February 3, 2014.

Filmed by Matthew Alston, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
